<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/1532181-i-am-still-reading-listening-to-this-book">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[I am still reading(listening) to this book and basically enjoying it. I found it absurd though that someone who will be gone from his condo for six months leaves the fridge stocked with raw meet, fresh veggies and herbs. Did I miss something here? (I do fall asleep sometimes and have to rewind, so it is possible.) <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
